# ---- Credentials + secrets ----
# If any of these ever appear in the repo root, something is wrong.
.env
.env.*
*.env
!*.env.example
credentials.txt
credentials.yaml
credentials.yml
secrets.txt
secrets.yaml
secrets.yml
*.pem
*.key
